query:
SELECT
                backup_id_pks.pk_json AS "id_pk: Value",
                organization_pks.pk_json  AS "org_pk: Value"
            FROM backup_id_pks
            LEFT JOIN organization_pks
                ON backup_id_pks.org_pk_id = organization_pks.id
            WHERE decode(backup_id_pks.pk_json #>>'{key}', 'hex') = $1
